==Documentation==
Renders the page chrome (hero, tabs) for an entity's /Images subpage.

Works for all entity types: Games, Characters, Companies, Concepts, Franchises,
Platforms, People, Locations, Objects, Genres, Themes, Accessories, DLCs, and Releases.

The Lua module determines the entity type from the page path prefix, queries the
parent page's SMW properties, and renders the appropriate hero and tab navigation
with the '''Images''' tab active.

===Usage===
<pre>
{{ImagesPage}}

== Screenshots ==
<gb-gallery>
0/628/267079-some-image.jpg | Optional caption
</gb-gallery>

{{ImagesPageEnd}}
</pre>

===Structure===
This template opens the following div structure (matching entity templates):
* <code>.gb-{type}-page</code> (opened around this template by MediaWiki parser)
* <code>.gb-{type}-hero</code>
* <code>.gb-{type}-tabs</code>
* <code>.gb-{type}-content .gb-images-content</code>
* <code>.gb-{type}-main .gb-images-main</code>
* <code>.gb-{type}-wiki-content</code>
</noinclude><includeonly>{{#invoke:ImagesPage|render}}</includeonly>
